\u160\'3f \u160\'3f \u160\'3f \u160\'3f \u160\'3f The Legislature shall provide for the establishment and maintenance of the state\rquote s education systems including: (a) a public education system, which shall be open to all children of the state; and (b) a higher education system.  Both systems shall be free from sectarian control.
\par 
}
